\par\pard\plain \tx0\tx360\tx720\tx1080\tx1440\tx1800\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\fi360\ltrch\loch \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Two hours, and more than 180 targets later, Marcus slumped onto the floor, still grinning like a madman. His mana and stamina were almost completely drained and his staff had vanished, but he was more than happy with his gains from the evaluation in both skills and stats. He\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92d gained five skill evolutions, with three of them granting an additional point of Dexterity, and new titles.}
